&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;pure-u-1&#34;&gt;
  &lt;img class=&#34;pure-img&#34; src=&#34;http://wyb0.com/img/post/global_agent_proxifier_set_rules2.png&#34; alt=&#34;Windows下实现全局代理-设置规则2.png&#34;&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

